b'Did you know there are 40m unused gadgets in UK homes, but 700,000 kids don\xe2\x80\x99t even have one? \xe2\x81\xa3\n\xe2\x81\xa3\nHelp the #GreatBritishTechAppeal by searching Great British Tech Appeal and donating today!'

b'Care Workers as well as all NHS Staff now qualify for 6 months of free unlimited data :clapping_hands:

So if you, or someone you know can benefit, go to keepconnected.vodafone.co.uk by June 6 to register :memo: :check_mark: Just a little help to say a big thank you.

#KeepingTheUKConnected'

b'Every day we\xe2\x80\x99re working hard at #KeepingTheUKConnected so that even when we\xe2\x80\x99re apart, nothing can stop us being together.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Help us support @britishredcross by texting CONNECT to 70141 to give \xc2\xa35 to help vulnerable people across the UK. Kindness will keep us together!\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Terms apply: redcross.org.uk/terms'

b'Keeping the UK connected is our top priority during these difficult times.\xe2\x81\xa3\n\xe2\x81\xa3\nWe\xe2\x80\x99re providing free access to NHS sites, increasing network capacity and providing tips to keep you connected. follow the link in our bio to find out more: @vodafoneuk'
